   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <opener><dateline><date when="1922-09-01">September 1, 1922</date></dateline><salute>Dear <persName key="richard_aldington">Richard</persName>:</salute></opener><p>
            This is to introduce to you a young man, a friend of mine, <persName key="royall_snow">Royall Snow</persName>. He is one of the Rhodes scholars at <orgName key="oxford">Oxford</orgName>, and I have known him for some years – since he was an undergraduate at <orgName key="harvard">Harvard</orgName>. I need hardly say that anything that you can do to make his sojourn in <placeName key="england">England</placeName> a pleasant one will be greatly appreciated by me.</p>
         <closer>Affectionately yours,</closer>
      </div>
   </body>
